text: Spiritual Kung-Fu () (Quan Jing) is a 1978 Hong Kong Taiwanese action movie directed by Lo Wei and starring Jackie Chan, Kao Kuang, Dean Shek, James Tien, Yee Fat, Yuen Biao. ==Other websites== * * Category:1978 action movies Category:Hong Kong action movies Category:Taiwanese movies Category:Golden Harvest movies Category:Movies directed by Lo Wei
